"uid":99299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2b43cacdb0cae3f260a862d1cd235258abc7e1b","tid":2126034,"uid":86441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T15:12:45.000Z","msg":"有個有情緒病哥哥，佢想睇醫生，但係太驚，驚到出唔到街，又返唔到工. 之前有揾過社工，但係都幫唔到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日日屋企都嘈咬，其實真係好攰，有無人明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望有其他方法幫到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T14:41:43.000Z","msg":"樓主 我都明啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又要照顧哥哥 但係又唔知點幫佢真係好無力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如講多啲，哥哥點解唔睇醫生？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6358b26ab220f504bb80cbbcc3fb32c8a08aa2","tid":2126034,"uid":136797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T15:26:53.000Z","msg":"直接放棄佢<br />\n唔好比佢習慣同倚賴"},{"pid":"f60aeb367df1422c3ad512e5d7771a89014dba47","tid":2126034,"uid":86441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ef4850cda630eda0da178e57fa945b642112ef9","tid":2126034,"uid":68478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T15:27:37.000Z","msg":"唔係嘅身邊都有個咁嘅人<br />\n要投其所好先同佢傾到計㗎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T04:38:01.000Z","msg":"同佢傾到計呀～不過佢真係好驚出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1bea5a15e15be73dd9c786fcc21fb1019f3aeaa","tid":2126034,"uid":86441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97beea59e62e298557d07db4b659c02e6e9a23f1","tid":2126034,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T17:06:57.000Z","msg":"佢返過工?<br />\n咩病?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T04:39:34.000Z","msg":"返過工，第一次睇醫生話係情緒病，之後佢唔肯去睇，又話好驚，唔知係咪驚恐症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6d339a09f632d51d57bbe8219fb627d7f934f23","tid":2126034,"uid":86441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59ad2b7d8049a7b1c29ee2282ea8f0d412c765a7","tid":2126034,"uid":350158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2b43cacdb0cae3f260a862d1cd235258abc7e1b","tid":2126034,"uid":86441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T15:12:45.000Z","msg":"有個有情緒病哥哥，佢想睇醫生，但係太驚，驚到出唔到街，又返唔到工. 之前有揾過社工，但係都幫唔到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日日屋企都嘈咬，其實真係好攰，有無人明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望有其他方法幫到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T02:44:40.000Z","msg":"陪佢去睇醫生啦 拖實佢隻手 會有安全感啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T04:40:16.000Z","msg":"咁做佢更加唔會出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"995605e0007adffb9bed8be6f028b29d6104223a","tid":2126034,"uid":86441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcdad97a1f72cec97d8155fcef058212898c3b07","tid":2126034,"uid":132810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:55:52.000Z","msg":"以前有個女同學，簡直係中學陰影。<br />\n<br />\n留班生。初開學，覺得佢個人冇咩野，所以同佢FD。<br />\n點知之後成日冇端端鬧人，<br />\n係勁大聲嗰隻。搞到啲人真係比佢嚇到彈起！<br />\n<br />\n明明冇問題嘅野，佢都可以搵到問題。（唔知係未你呀哥嗰種。）<br />\n我同人傾普通閒計，佢會無端端鬧我。<br />\n<br />\n其實學校留得佢班，即一早知佢有病。<br />\n佢有病，我唔歧視佢，但好心跟進得好啲。唔好等我地學生自己講。<br />\n<br />\n最後學期尾，仲要呃哂我地全班錢。<br />\n<br />\nOP，我遇過幾個依種病人，所以明你煩惱。<br />\n不過你哥始終係家人，唔好怪佢。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T04:41:47.000Z","msg":"係呀～佢一發作就搞到成家人都唔開心，我怕呢個病會傳染，呀媽已經開始負面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0187b292453c6d1ac55083d7f1a240262390389","tid":2126034,"uid":86441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{